news: [Thanks to GitHub contributors] Anyone can contribute, do code review, improve documentation and create pull request. Share your contribution and add a Star to GitHub on https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection
[Contribute to the wiki] Open a pull request to improve documentation on https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection/wiki
[Test reports] Auto-generated reports are now published in the wiki, review Maven site and reports on https://ron190.github.io/jsql-injection/site/index.html

[Warning] An unverified app version is shared by platform Tryhackme in the room Advanced SQL Injection, please be careful downloading software from this platform. To contribute please ask Tryhackme to fix the room description, also in the meantime remember to always download official version from GitHub project page on https://github.com/ron190/jsql-injection
